                     <interp inst="t18220109-114-person1021" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner was brought to the office, I took him in change.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I told him I dare not take my Christmas-box till the 9th or 10th.</p>
